text:
Cheers, should have some footage, finally, tomorrow.. more so on the other project I'm doing so if I could send you a link to watch it for feedback that would be awesome! It's around 7 seconds long.
Just waiting for some 3D stuff to render today so hopefully that's done in a few hours.
Hate the waiting around part tension kills me :joy:

So got the first version of one of my projects, this one is based on the idea that a cult was using the room in the past but they've not used it for a while so it needs to be a bit dusty etc.. 
I want to put a skeleton in the cage but that's the last thing on my list right now.
So far I've just messed around with the colour, cage and one symbol on the floor. 

<https://youtu.be/dhxPQFj0PCU|https://youtu.be/dhxPQFj0PCU>

If you think that something's off or not quite right please be as critical as you need too be!
